OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FVapes are to be put in plain packaging
OL,7,Funder proposals which aim to stop the
OL,8,Fdevices being marketed to children.
OL,10,FHealth leaders have launched a
OL,11,Fconsultation which also proposes that
OL,12,Fvape devices can only come in three
OL,13,Fcolours: white, black or grey.
OL,15,FThe UK-wide proposals will also see
OL,16,Frestrictions on flavour descriptions
OL,17,Fusing simple names such as "apple"
OL,18,Fwhile banning names relating to
OL,19,Fsweets, desserts and alcohol.
OL,26,@yD@\OUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
