FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FThe consultation also sets out plans
OL,7,Fto keep vapes out of sight in shops,
OL,8,Fthe Department of Health and Social
OL,9,FCare said.
OL,11,FAnnouncing the plans, Health Secretary
OL,12,FJames Murray said: "Today, we're
OL,13,Flaunching a 12-week consultation about
OL,14,Four plans to make vaping less
OL,15,Fattractive to children and young
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,26,@tD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,F"We all recognise that vaping has a
OL,7,Frole to play for adults to stop
OL,8,Fsmoking... but I don't think any of us
OL,9,Fwant children and young people to
OL,10,Fstart vaping in the first place.
OL,12,F"A lot of the marketing is designed in
OL,13,Fa way where it's very colourful, some
OL,14,Fof the names are clearly aimed at
OL,15,Fchildren and young people - that's
OL,16,Fwhat we want to take on.
OL,18,F"We want to make sure that, as well as
OL,19,Fbeing a smoke-free generation, we want
OL,20,Fchildren and young people not to start
OL,21,Fvaping in the first place."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,F'We want children and young people not
OL,7,Fto start vaping in the first place',
OL,8,Fsaid James Murray.
OL,10,FFigures suggest that almost one in
OL,11,Ffive (19%) 11`17-year-olds in Britain
OL,12,Fhave tried vaping, according to a poll
OL,13,Fconducted on behalf of the charity
OL,14,FAction on Smoking and Health (Ash).
OL,16,FEngland's chief medical officer,
OL,17,FProfessor Sir Chris Whitty, has said
OL,18,Fin the past that marketing vapes to
OL,19,Fchildren is "utterly unacceptable".
OL,26,@{D@MOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FProfessor Steve Turner, president of
OL,7,Fthe Royal College of Paediatrics and
OL,8,FChild Health, welcomed the
OL,9,Fconsultation, adding: "For those of us
OL,10,Fworking with children every day, it is
OL,11,Fclear that only strong and meaningful
OL,12,Fregulation will protect them from the
OL,13,Fharms associated with nicotine
OL,14,Faddiction."
OL,16,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,17,FCare said that the consultation
OL,18,Fincludes plans for white packaging for
OL,19,Fvapes with restrictions on text
OL,20,Fcolour, imagery, branding and
OL,21,Fstandardised product information.
OL,26,@qD@WOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
