OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FOfficials said that the move follows
OL,7,Fthe success of standardised packaging
OL,8,Ffor cigarettes since 2017.
OL,10,FThe consultation also proposes inserts
OL,11,Ffor cigarette packs telling them where
OL,12,Fto get help to quit and plans to make
OL,13,Fall tobacco products ` including
OL,14,Fcigarette rolling paper and cigars `
OL,15,Fcome in plain packaging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
