OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FThe proposals also include plans to
OL,7,Fremove exemptions which allow duty-
OL,8,Ffree shops and airports to display
OL,9,Ftobacco products, meaning cigarettes
OL,10,Fand other tobacco products will be
OL,11,Frestricted from view in these settings.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FResearch published last year concluded
OL,19,Fthat adults are still likely to buy e-
OL,20,Fcigarettes sold in plain packs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
