OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FThe study, led by UCL and King's
OL,7,FCollege London researchers, involved
OL,8,F2,770 children and young people aged
OL,9,F11 to 18 and just under 4,000 adults.
OL,11,FThey were shown vape packs and
OL,12,Fchildren were asked about whether they
OL,13,Ffelt their peers would be interested
OL,14,Fin trying the product, while adults
OL,15,Fwere asked if they themselves would be
OL,16,Finterested in trying it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1783673386
OL,3,CVapes to be put in plain packaging in
OL,4,Cbid to crack down on appeal to children
OL,6,FAmong the children and young people
OL,7,Fquestioned, half (53%) said their
OL,8,Fpeers would be interested in trying
OL,9,Fvapes in their usual packaging,
OL,10,Faccording to the study, which was
OL,11,Fpublished in the Lancet Regional
OL,12,FHealth Europe.
OL,14,FThis dropped to 38% when they were
OL,15,Fshown vapes in standardised packs with
OL,16,Fusual flavour descriptions.
OL,18,FAmong adults, interest remained
OL,19,Fsimilar whether packs were
OL,20,Fstandardised in white or branded
OL,21,Fpacking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
